366
00:24:05,677 --> 00:24:07,109
Maafkan aku.

367
00:24:07,111 --> 00:24:08,278
Tak apa.

368
00:24:08,280 --> 00:24:10,314
Semuanya akan membaik.

369
00:24:10,316 --> 00:24:12,581
